====Pokémon Adventures====
{{main|Crystal (Adventures)}}
Crystal from [[Pokémon Adventures]] is based on Kris's design. She is unique among all [[Pokédex holder]]s in the sense that her primary goal is to fill the [[Pokédex]], getting hired to do so by {{adv|Professor Oak}} and becoming his {{TP|Professor|assistant}}. She is an expert in {{pkmn2|Caught|catching}} Pokémon and prefers to kick the [[Poké Ball]]s she uses instead of throwing them. During the {{MangaArc|HeartGold & SoulSilver}}, she involuntarily dons a new outfit based on {{ga|Lyra}}'s clothes, making her Lyra's Pokémon Adventures counterpart as well.
